title: 6 Min Daily Pilates Abs Workout (No Equipment)
description:
Join me in this 6 minute Pilates abs workout. Its up to you whether you choose to perform this workout daily, a few times per week or mix it up with your other workouts.

General disclaimer
Any form of exercise involves a risk of injury, especially when performed incorrectly or with poor form. I am a qualified personal trainer and nutrition coach. Should you have any existing medical conditions or health concerns please consult a medical doctor before performing any exercises or implementing nutritional advice provided Jenna Collins Fitness.
I do not guarantee results from any of my workouts. Each person is different and will get different results from any workout they perform. Regular exercise combined consistent good nutrition habits is key to getting results.
channelDescription:
Short home workouts combining Pilates, HIIT & Strength Training 

Welcome! I'm a certified personal trainer and nutrition coach through ISSA (International Sports Science Association).
I am also an ex ballet, tap & jazz dancer of 25 years. I decided to create this channel to help people anywhere in the world lose weight & tone their physique through short home workouts and bodyweight. I want to make exercising fun, convenient and most of all, get you incredible results! You do not need equipment or a gym membership to get in the best shape of your life.

Remember to subscribe & turn notifications on so you never miss a workout! 

Business contact: support@jennacollinsfitness.com
